      "components": [
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-absolute-zero:#ffffff;--color-pitch-black:#000000;--color-shadow-play:#e0e0e0;--color-concrete-gray:#999999;--color-pebble:#cccccc;--font-adineue:system-ui,sans-serif;--font-arial:Arial,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;width:600px;background:var(--color-absolute-zero);border:1px solid var(--color-shadow-play);border-radius:3px;padding:32px 40px;font-family:var(--font-adineue);text-align:center;\">\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom:12px;\">\n    <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-adineue);font-size:14px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-concrete-gray);line-height:1.4;\">Reference Error: 0.97d73b17.1775933003.25512cae</span>\n  </div>\n  <h1 style=\"font-family:var(--font-adineue);font-size:23px;font-weight:700;color:var(--color-pitch-black);line-height:1.4;margin:0 0 20px 0;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:normal;\">Unfortunately we are unable to give you access to our site at this time.</h1>\n  <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-adineue);font-size:17px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-pitch-black);line-height:1.4;margin:0 auto;max-width:480px;\">A security issue was automatically identified, when you tried to access the website.</p>\n</div>",
          "name": "Error Alert Banner",
          "role": "",
          "description": ""
        },
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-absolute-zero:#ffffff;--color-pitch-black:#000000;--color-shadow-play:#e0e0e0;--color-concrete-gray:#999999;--color-pebble:#cccccc;--font-adineue:system-ui,sans-serif;--font-arial:Arial,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;width:600px;background:var(--color-absolute-zero);display:flex;gap:0;border-top:1px solid var(--color-shadow-play);\">\n  <div style=\"flex:1;padding:32px 28px;border-right:1px solid var(--color-shadow-play);text-align:center;\">\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:var(--font-adineue);font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--color-pitch-black);line-height:1.4;margin:0 0 20px 0;\">What could have caused this?</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-adineue);font-size:14px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-pitch-black);line-height:1.4;margin:0;\">During high-traffic product releases we have extra security in place to prevent bots entering our site. We do this to protect customers and to give everyone a fair chance of getting the sneakers. Something in your setup must have triggered our security system, so we cannot allow you onto the site.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"flex:1;padding:32px 28px;text-align:center;\">\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:var(--font-adineue);font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--color-pitch-black);line-height:1.4;margin:0 0 20px 0;\">How can I resolve this?</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-adineue);font-size:14px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-pitch-black);line-height:1.4;margin:0 0 16px 0;\">Please try refreshing or accessing our website from a different browser or another device. You could also check if there are any scripts, like ad blockers, running in your browser and disable them.</p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-adineue);font-size:14px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-pitch-black);line-height:1.4;margin:0;\">If this does not help, the issue might be caused by malware. If you're on a personal connection you can run an anti-virus scan on your device to make sure it's not affected by malware.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>",
          "name": "Two-Column Info Cards",
          "role": "",
          "description": ""
        },
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-absolute-zero:#ffffff;--color-pitch-black:#000000;--color-shadow-play:#e0e0e0;--color-concrete-gray:#999999;--color-pebble:#cccccc;--font-adineue:system-ui,sans-serif;--font-arial:Arial,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;width:600px;background:var(--color-absolute-zero);padding:40px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:16px;border:1px solid var(--color-shadow-play);\">\n  <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-adineue);font-size:17px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-pitch-black);line-height:1.4;margin:0 0 8px 0;text-align:center;\">Need help getting back on track?</p>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;\">\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:var(--color-pitch-black);color:var(--color-absolute-zero);font-family:var(--font-arial);font-size:16px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.2;padding:14px 32px;border:1px solid var(--color-pitch-black);border-radius:3px;text-decoration:none;text-align:center;\">Try Again</a>\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:var(--color-absolute-zero);color:var(--color-pitch-black);font-family:var(--font-arial);font-size:16px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.2;padding:14px 32px;border:1px solid var(--color-pitch-black);border-radius:3px;text-decoration:none;text-align:center;\">Learn More</a>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:8px;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid var(--color-shadow-play);width:100%;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;\">\n    <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Enter your email address\" style=\"flex:1;background:var(--color-absolute-zero);color:var(--color-pitch-black);font-family:var(--font-arial);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.2;padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--color-pebble);border-radius:3px;outline:none;\" />\n    <button style=\"background:var(--color-pitch-black);color:var(--color-absolute-zero);font-family:var(--font-arial);font-size:16px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.2;padding:8px 20px;border:1px solid var(--color-pitch-black);border-radius:3px;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;\">Notify Me</button>\n  </div>\n</div>",
